Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fe134}{\fsp0}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(190,278)}{\fn方正准圆简体}{\bord0}{\fs20}{\c&H24EFFF&}宇宙大探索\n{\fs17}{\c&HFFFFFF&} 第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:41.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的身世很神秘\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We were born into a mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:43.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一直困扰着我们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one that has haunted us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自从人类诞生就是如此\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}since at least as long as we've been human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:51.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这个星空覆盖下的小星球上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We awakened on this tiny world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们开始有了意识\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beneath a blanket of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就如同被遗弃在门口的婴儿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like an abandoned baby left on a doorstep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有留下只字词组\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without a note to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我们是谁 我们从哪里来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where we came from, who we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的世界会是怎样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how our universe came to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:10.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在宇宙中是否还有其它同类\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And with no idea how to end our cosmic isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:14.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们必须自己找出答案\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've had to figure it all out for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们最大的财富\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Best thing we had going for us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是我们的智慧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was our intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:27.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特别是识别规律的天赋\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}especially our gift for pattern recognition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经过远古以来进化过程的改造\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sharpened over eons of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些擅长区分猎物和猛兽的人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ones who were good at spotting prey and predator,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:36.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}擅长识别有毒的食物的人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}telling poisonous plants from the nourishing ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们活下去并繁衍的几率更大\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they had a better chance to live and reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:43.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们幸存下来 并把识别规律的基因传下去\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They survived and passed on those genes for pattern recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}优势显而易见\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with its obvious advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球上的不同文化\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cultures all over the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是仰望同一个星空\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looked up at the same stars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后做出不同的解读\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and found different pictures there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们用这种天赋在自然界中寻找规律\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We used this gift for recognizing patterns in nature
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解读天空中的年历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to read the calendar in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}写在星空中的信息\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The messages written in the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我们的祖先\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}told our forefathers and mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何时安营  何时启程\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when to camp and when to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兽群何时迁徙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the migratory herds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何时下雨  何时天寒\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and when the rains and the cold would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何时他们可以停下来休息\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when they would cease for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当他们观察恒星间的运动与地球上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When they observed the direct connection between the motions of the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命周期变化之间的直接联系\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the seasonal cycles of life on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们很自然地得出结论\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they concluded, naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天上发生的变化\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that what happens up there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必然和地球上发生的事情息息相关\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}must be directed at us down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有道理 对吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It makes sense, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果把天空看成日历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the sky was a calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人在上面贴上一张便签纸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and somebody stuck a Post-it note on top of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了传达信息还会是什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what else could it be but a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以  当天空的秩序被突然打破时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so, when the heavenly order was suddenly violated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如 当彗星划过天际时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the apparition of a comet in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们就会和自身联系起来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they took it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不能怪他们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can we really blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时 对于所发生的事情也没有其它\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Back then, they had no other logical explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}符合逻辑的解释\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是很久以前\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was long before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人会认为地球是个\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}anyone had yet to imagine Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倾斜自转的行星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a spinning planet with a tilted axis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绕着太阳公转\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}revolving around the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每种文化中的古人都犯过相同的错误\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every ancient human culture made the same mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彗星一定是来自众神\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a comet must be a message,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或某一个神的旨意\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sent by the gods... or one particular god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎是必然的  我们的祖先认为\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And almost invariably, our ancestors concluded
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事不妙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the news was not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论你是古阿兹特克人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It didn't matter if you were an ancient Aztec,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:28.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古英国人 古巴比伦人  古印度人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anglo-Saxon, Babylonian, Hindu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彗星都是毁灭的前兆\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Comets were portents of doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仅有的不同是\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The only difference among them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灾难预报的精确程度\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was the precise nature of the coming disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灾祸 源自希腊语中的 灾星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Dis-aster," as in the Greek word for "bad star."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对东非的马塞人来说\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the Masai of East Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彗星意味着饥荒\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a comet meant famine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对南非的祖鲁人来说\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the Zulu in the south,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意味着战争\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it meant war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于西非的迦纳人来说\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the Eghap people of the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意味着瘟疫\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it meant disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对扎伊尔人来说\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To the Djaga of Zaire,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}扎伊尔人（刚果）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特指 天花\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}specifically "smallpox."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于他们的邻居 陆巴人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To their neighbors, the Luba,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:03.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彗星预示着领袖之死\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a comet foretold the death of a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:07.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古代中国人有着惊人的系统分类\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ancient Chinese were remarkably systematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大约公元前1400年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Starting in roughly 1400 BC,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们就开始了对彗星的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they began recording and cataloguing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记录和分类\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the apparitions of comets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三尾彗星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A three-tailed comet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意味着国家的灾难\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}meant calamity for the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四尾彗星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A four-tailed comet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}标志着瘟疫降临\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}signified an epidemic was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类识别规律的天赋\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The human talent for pattern recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是把双刃剑\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a two-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们尤其擅长寻找规律\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're especially good at finding patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪怕无中生有\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even when they aren't really there--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者 牵强附会\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}something known as "false pattern recognition."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们渴望证明\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We hunger for significance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的存在对这个宇宙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for signs that our personal existence
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有着重大的意义\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is of special meaning to the universe.
